Functions to run the BARD method as described in 

"Bayesian detection of abnormal segments in multiple time series"

by Lawrence Bardwell and Prof Paul Fearnhead

######
example.R - gives a step by step example on using BARD with a simulated dataset from sim_from_model.R with parameters from params.R

The folder bayesian contains code that calculates the posterior using approximate recursions.

The folder get_samples contains code to sample from this posterior
